introduction:
It’s week 8, the standings are an absolute cluster fuck and I am running out of jokes to make. Rankings are pretty easy these days, just keep Marquin at number 1 and make sure to keep me and Dylan at the very bottom. 

 Will a favorite emerge before playoffs begin? 

 Will we see anymore blockbuster trades before the deadline? 

 Will someone step up and help me write these rankings so I’m not busting my balls every week? 

 Week 8 Power Rankings, let’s go.
